{"TopicId":4891,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Changing rockets command module","CreatedByName":"Splendid","CreatedById":3722,"CreatedDateTime":"2011-12-27T17:06:58Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Splendid","CreatedById":3722,"CreatedDateTime":"2011-12-27T17:06:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI have a rocket, I want to change its command module since it would be easier to navigate around the moon as a rover, but I don\\\u0027t feel like re-creating the entire rocket just for a command module, is there any way to change it without making a new rocket?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Capt\u0026#039;n Skunky","CreatedById":1261,"CreatedDateTime":"2011-12-27T17:12:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EEdit the .craft file. Just change the information for the current capsule to one of the others. To see what you need to change, view another .craft file that uses the capsule you want.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EArrr!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECapt\\\u0027n Skunky\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Splendid","CreatedById":3722,"CreatedDateTime":"2011-12-27T17:16:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDo I use notepad to edit it? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2011-12-27T18:07:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Splendid\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Splendid\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDo I use notepad to edit it? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003EObviously, unless there is something else you would like to use.\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Capt\u0026#039;n Skunky","CreatedById":1261,"CreatedDateTime":"2011-12-27T18:08:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Splendid\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Splendid\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDo I use notepad to edit it? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E.craft files are simple text files. Nothing fancy required.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EArrr!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECapt\\\u0027n Skunky\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Splendid","CreatedById":3722,"CreatedDateTime":"2011-12-27T18:14:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThanks a-lot mate \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}